Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.48,Default-alt,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:33.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:35.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Colonel Mustang did something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:36.78,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:37.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just a rumor I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.03,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Turn on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.24,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,"Radio Capital"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.08,Default,Master,0000,0000,0000,,Radio Capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There's something crazy going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.71,Default,Master,0000,0000,0000,,That station is so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Before the military stops the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:54.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.35,Radio,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right, Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.10,Radio,Master,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:04.93,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:09.35,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Army tried to murder me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So they pointed a gun at you to shoot you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.11,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:24.99,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Kill her along with Colonel Mustang's men."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:29.00,Radio,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Führer President Bradley is currently in the east for an inspection,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.75,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,and is not in Central at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.25,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.42,Radio,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So do you suppose someone in the upper echelon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.67,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,is planning a coup d'etat while the Führer President is absent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.01,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is this truly the real Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.06,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize this voice, though. She's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:50.69,Radio,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But Madam, the fact that your son was also not in Central at the time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.90,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get in touch with my son either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.52,Radio,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.61,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.15,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Selim's safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.66,Radio,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Please get yourself together, Madam Bradley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A coup d'etat, they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.49,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we are thankful that you're safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:07.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think anyone other than Bradley would be able to keep this nation together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:14.00,Radio,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,If Colonel Mustang hadn't saved me,\NI don't even know if I'd be here right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:19.05,Radio,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so Colonel Mustang had already predicted the coup d'etat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.38,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:25.30,Radio,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, could you please describe in detail of what happened when you were rescued?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.68,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:32.02,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Have you still not told her that Selim is a homunculus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:33.85,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,A gun was pointed at me, so I closed my eyes and began saying my prayers to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.27,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,How could we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.19,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't even know that her husband is currently missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:38.40,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard a gun go off, I thought everything was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:39.69,Radio,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.32,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,We hadn't told you this yet, Madam,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:50.66,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,but the thing is, the train that the Führer President was on yesterday in the east was bombed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.58,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.29,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Bradley!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:02.97,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:09.72,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,I-It appears as though Madam Bradley is feeling ill due to shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:15.02,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,But the Führer President has gone missing?\NWhat could this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.36,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang has always been leery of the upper echelon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.87,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,and was anticipating that they'd pull something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.49,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when the Führer President's train was bombed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.29,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, an order to shoot the Madam was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.58,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:39.59,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,There is a faction in the upper echelon that wants to get rid of the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.09,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.97,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and stop the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.84,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Be well-prepared for the consequences if you refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.10,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:56.85,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken hostages, and we can hardly move due to the fact that they've got a gun on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:01.82,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,And for starters, there are so many of them that we don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.49,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to Mustang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.36,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to him directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.24,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.24,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,The... Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.08,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.34,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.10,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like my acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.23,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,It was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.27,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, keep the show airing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:39.77,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.23,Default,Pro,0000,0000,0000,,Like we can let a scoop like this go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.57,Radio,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we will have one of Colonel Mustang's subordinates speak with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.16,Radio,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,She also participated in the mission to rescue the Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't the Colonel who planned the coup d'etat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.41,Radio,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,We, who support Colonel Mustang, have very little influence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This... voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.37,Radio,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,...but inheriting the Führer President's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:02.88,Radio,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,we are prepared to stand up to our underhanded opponents with everything we've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.92,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.30,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,That damned Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:17.77,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Bradley isn't around, he's exploiting the hell out of the Führer President's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.81,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,And bringing up words like 'justice'...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.53,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if the people would take his bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.53,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,You sounded like you're used to this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.58,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you could use a silly and vague word like 'justice'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.91,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.54,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone loves justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.96,Default,Char,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.79,Default,Char,0000,0000,0000,,The first person to say it wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.30,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's not Mustang and his men's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.09,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:51.14,Default,Ish,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang is telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.47,Default,Ish,0000,0000,0000,,We just arrived here from the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:59.10,Default,Ish,0000,0000,0000,,but there was a huge ruckus over there\Nabout the Führer President's train being blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.36,Default,Ish2,0000,0000,0000,,Do the people at Central still not know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:08.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The highest-ranking man in the nation is missing, and they still haven't bothered to tell its people anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.11,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,So it really {\i1}is{\i0} a coup d'etat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.49,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.62,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,If Radio Capital happens to be ambushed and the Madam gets killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.37,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,it's obviously the upper echelon who's behind it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Selim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.17,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably being taken hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.88,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.26,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are the guards doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.34,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.76,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the enemy was in possession of more firearms than they'd expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're putting up a bitter fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:41.89,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be limit to how many firearms they can carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We have a call from the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:46.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.65,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long to contact us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.19,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:50.82,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,W-We had no idea the men from Briggs were in possession of such-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.08,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will we be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they'll take control of this place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.09,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.59,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... what fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.05,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to have to bring in something like a tank to-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:13.97,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.47,Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I lend you a hand, Fullmetal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've made some new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, this place brings back memories, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of your crying face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see honest tears like that from you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.79,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you despised liquids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Since they make you useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.68,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Save the chatting for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.51,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Take them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.68,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.47,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,We need to defeat these pale things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Bullets aren't enough to bring them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.56,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,That again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.90,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.53,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No, their wounds aren't recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But they don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Must be the power of a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They are enemies, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.38,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Running around like a cockroach...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.05,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he doesn't want me going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.05,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,That sensation also grows larger as I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.05,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.46,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, May?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.09,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:01.89,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.64,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you return to your country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:06.77,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.31,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,B-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.56,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Because...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.10,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.73,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Mister Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.61,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Human traits like this make my skin crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:27.91,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, looks like you guys showed them who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:32.67,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The Fullmetal Alchemist and the Flame Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.25,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The shitty chimeras I owe a favor to from up north are with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:42.47,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now... I wonder who I should take care of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Envy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Homunculus that can change form, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.77,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.06,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.23,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.57,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay, Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:01.15,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's a State Alchemist who turned Ishbal into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.66,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.24,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're all buddy-buddy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.41,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Show me something more muddy and disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:17.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I find enjoyment in watching you pieces of trash shrieking like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.05,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to entertain your vulgar hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.47,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Vulgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.80,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let me ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:33.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you humans also love watching people's unhappiness and watching fools dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.06,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're always fighting wars?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,True, it is indeed entertaining to watch fools dance like madmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:51.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's especially entertaining to watch fools like you homunculi dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.87,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I answered your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time for you to answer mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Who killed Maes Hughes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.77,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Maria Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.69,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The one you burned to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So you basically burned an innocent woman alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.03,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.24,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.91,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you explain it to her family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you cry and beg for mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:36.21,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you perhaps refrain from saying anything because you were afraid of how furious they'd be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Were you never taught to shut your mouth, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:45.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get tired of asking you homunculi the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Simply state the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Who killed Hughes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.12,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Colonel Mustang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You finally found the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:27.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine Hughes getting killed by a moron like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.84,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,'Moron'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.68,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Morons are what you'd call...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.77,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...idiots like Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who'd fall for dumb shit like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Your face changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.28,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I love that expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.87,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes had a great look on his face when I killed him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.66,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:01.12,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The despair of being killed by someone who looks just like his beloved wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.00,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.88,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who killed Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.48,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say anything else, Envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start this by...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...reducing your tongue to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.21,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this place to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's {\i1}my{\i0} prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.76,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.39,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll leave this place to you and go on-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.43,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.77,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I still need to repay the debt you guys gave me up north-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:11.45,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the time to be speaking to others while facing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:17.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there's quite a lot of fat on that blabbering tongue of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It burns quite well, Envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, will it really be okay-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.46,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something you need to take care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.05,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:38.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.77,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a....!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.27,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:54.15,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing off a homunculus\Nshould be a piece of cake for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.03,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.24,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.83,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you've been seeking revenge for Hughes' death the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.72,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:34.53,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Out of respect for that beautiful friendship, I'll fight you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:38.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't really hold back when fighting in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.03,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me for any-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to have all the liquids within your eyes boil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The pain goes far beyond anything you could possibly imagine, doesn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.17,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You little-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It was nice of you to make yourself a bigger target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.72,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could beat me if you increased your size?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:02.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you repeat this suffering until you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.02,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.32,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.32,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who burned Lust to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.66,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dispose of him on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.26,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.55,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,These things look creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.35,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,They're almost like veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:46.22,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I keep having this nasty feeling, like I'm having heartburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.56,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:52.69,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge cluster of energy ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.07,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Cluster of energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:19:00.49,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Would you get it if I described it as an insane number of people crawling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.87,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, but I do understand that it feels disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:11.04,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate to encounter an enemy in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Scar, do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.67,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Is this about the Flame Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:29.68,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Because I once lost my soul after engulfing myself in flames of revenge, I can understand well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.44,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,If he goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:37.69,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,...he'll end up reducing even his own heart with the flames of wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Envy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.05,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come out, you'll be seeing another huge explosion from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.93,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.60,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're human after all! Let this throw you into confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:19.36,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You'd set your best friend aflame without hesitation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.20,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions do nothing more than feeding oil to flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.58,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so cocky!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.05,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes... My eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You came at me, thinking I wouldn't use much firepower if you were near me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, I can pinpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, I'm going to have to disobey your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're disobeying my orders, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.62,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't just stand there and wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:01.84,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Envy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:05.09,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This place is like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave my side, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:10.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're here, I'm going to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:00.41,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment someone is born,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:04.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they gradually become more and more human as time goes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:10.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And what has been accumulated eventually becomes complete as a strong self.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:12.34,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.59,0:24:17.81,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:21.27,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 54, Beyond the Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:25.61,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Peer once more at your heart.
